{"word":"G2593 - καρποφόρος - karpophóros - kar-pof-or'-os - Fruitful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καρποφόρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">karpophóros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kar-pof-or'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fruitful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"செழிப்புள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"fruit - bearing, fruitful, productive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2590 - καρπός - karpós - kar-pos'/2590\">G2590</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; <i>fruitbearing</i> (figuratively): - fruitful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G175/175\">G175</a>, <a href=\"#/G2590/2590\">G2590</a>, <a href=\"#/G2591/2591\">G2591</a>, <a href=\"#/G2592/2592\">G2592</a>, <a href=\"#/G2593/2593\">G2593</a>"}]}